{
    "maqras": [
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "He frowned and turned away"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "because the blind man came to him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "What will make you realize that he may [yet] be purified (of disbelief)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "or even reminded, and the Reminder may benefit him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "However anyone who seems indifferent"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "you will attend to"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "It is not your concern whether he will purify himself (or not)"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "Yet with someone who comes to you eagerly"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "and anxiously"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "you act so distracted"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "Indeed, it serves as a Reminder"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "Anyone who wishes should remember how it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "[exists] on honored pages"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "which are held aloft [for display], cleansed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "by the hands of noble, virtuous scribes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "noble, virtuous"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "Let man be damned! What makes him act ungrateful"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "From what sort of thing did He create him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "From a drop of semen has He created him and proportioned him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "Then He made the Way easy for him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "next He will let him die and bury him"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Then [later on] He will raise him up again whenever He may wish"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "Of course he does not accomplish what He orders him to"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "So let man look at his own food"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "We let water pour down abundantly"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "then We split the earth right open"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "and cause grain to sprout from it"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "and grapes and fodder"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "olive trees, datepalms"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 30,
            "text": "and dense woodlots"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 31,
            "text": "and fruit[-trees) and pastures"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 32,
            "text": "as an enjoyment for both you and your livestock"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 33,
            "text": "When the uproar comes"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 34,
            "text": "on a day when man will flee from his brother"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 35,
            "text": "his mother and his father"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 36,
            "text": "his mate and his children"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 37,
            "text": "every last man among them will have enough concern that day to keep him occupied"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 38,
            "text": "Some faces will be beaming on that day"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 39,
            "text": "laughing, rejoicing"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 40,
            "text": "while other faces will be covered with grime on that day"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 41,
            "text": "soot will overshadow them"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 80,
            "verse": 42,
            "text": "Those will be the shameless disbelievers"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 1,
            "text": "When the sun has been extinguished"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 2,
            "text": "when the stars slip out of place"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 3,
            "text": "when the mountains travel along"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 4,
            "text": "when ten-month pregnant camels are neglected"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 5,
            "text": "when wild beasts are herded together"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 6,
            "text": "when the seas overflow"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 7,
            "text": "when souls are reunited"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 8,
            "text": "when the buried girl is asked"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 9,
            "text": "for what offence she has been killed"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 10,
            "text": "when scriptures are unrolled"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 11,
            "text": "when the sky is stripped bare"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 12,
            "text": "when Hades is set blazing"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 13,
            "text": "when the Garden is brought close"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 14,
            "text": "each soul shall know what it has prepared"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 15,
            "text": "So I swear by the planets"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 16,
            "text": "moving, sweeping along"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 17,
            "text": "and night as it draws on"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 18,
            "text": "and morn when it breathes again"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 19,
            "text": "it is a statement by a generous messenger"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 20,
            "text": "possessing strength established by the One Enthroned"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 21,
            "text": "Who is to be Obeyed and more than that is Trustworthy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 22,
            "text": "Your companion is not crazy"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 23,
            "text": "He saw him on the clear horizon"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 24,
            "text": "nor was he grudging about the Unseen"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 25,
            "text": "Nor is it a statement [made] by some outcast Satan"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 26,
            "text": "So where are you (all) heading for"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 27,
            "text": "It is merely a Reminder to [everyone in] the Universe"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 28,
            "text": "So anyone of you who wishes may go straight"
        },
        {
            "chapter": 81,
            "verse": 29,
            "text": "Yet you will only wish whatever God, Lord of the Universe, may wish"
        }
    ]
}